{"tid":1452712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排真係好撚多降溫撚 一有警犬做仆街野就衝出黎幫件事降溫 想滅左大家心中團火","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:38:41.000Z","uid":288670,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cca8cbcec1eda31135ddc7ab0f219499652d5bb","tid":1452712,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"自從天水圍女義士事件之後 降溫撚真係愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n呢班人成日用唔好俾仇恨支配做借口 試圖幫警犬做既全部仆街野去降溫 呢班人根本唔想抗爭成功 仲幾時都想滅左各義士心中團火 想將任何升級行動瓦解 <br />\n<br />\n無左團火仲何來抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"6faa4c42e12958b35b96862656170eb10f8fb0d1","tid":1452712,"uid":266993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"放心 冇人會理果班撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164d0c686e62f7dbfc1bf7de807277eb951b406b","tid":1452712,"uid":296350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n記者可唔可以有共識！！<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？點證明佢哋冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9565e6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=a8ccb96c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=3505d03f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=7beff1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=e95623cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a49696d801ebcbf147e19276515f111dc058bdd","tid":1452712,"uid":288272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"我有理由相信而家想降溫既只係左膠<br />\n因為林奠同肥聰做緊既所有回應都似乎係想升溫<br />\n唯恐天下不亂"},{"pid":"f294898d0a26005cc1c146ecc1ce9d3ab344d8ae","tid":1452712,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a1748a7d7a39aa6e89f9db0b11133ed064ca681","tid":1452712,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"},{"pid":"01d6eb42a0c0499b4fad09b1ffccda37cf9cfa51","tid":1452712,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1748a7d7a39aa6e89f9db0b11133ed064ca681","tid":1452712,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63993f8d52979dc6635e35bf9fc7d25bdea6436a","tid":1452712,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ce5a8e6719be38f834890bcca05da947b308443","tid":1452712,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a>"